title: Women Climbing Mountains
itunes:title: Women Climbing Mountains
description:
SMNTY's on top of the world! Since the dawn of people climbing mountains, women have been there, though their clothing and existence in the space has long been policed. We trace the triumphs and tragedies of women mountaineers, and efforts to make it more inclusive. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
